---
---

<section class="relative bg-navy text-white pt-[140px] pb-[80px] px-5 md:px-0 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Grid Background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-100" style="background-image: url('/bg/bg-grid-overlay.svg'); background-size: 32px 32px;"></div>
  
  <!-- Radial Glow -->
  <div class="absolute top-[-10%] right-[-10%] w-[600px] h-[600px] rounded-full blur-[120px] opacity-40 pointer-events-none" 
       style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(56,139,253,0.14) 0%, transparent 60%);">
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-container mx-auto reveal">
     <!-- Pill Badge -->
     <div class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-blue/40 text-blue text-[10px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider mb-8 bg-blue/5">
       Available for remote work worldwide
     </div>

     <!-- H1 -->
    <h1 class="text-[32px] md:text-[52px] font-bold font-display leading-[1.15] mb-6 max-w-[800px]">
      Your clinic is losing patients<br class="hidden md:block" /> 
      to a problem that has already<br class="hidden md:block" /> 
      been solved.
    </h1>

    <!-- Body Large -->
     <p class="text-[16px] md:text-[18px] text-white/70 font-body leading-[1.7] max-w-hero mb-10">
       Most private clinics run on WhatsApp, paper, and memory. 
       Every missed follow-up, every manual appointment, every 
       unanswered message is a patient — and revenue — walking 
       out the door. I build the systems that close that door.
     </p>

    <!-- Name Signature Block -->
    <div class="mt-8">
      <div class="w-10 h-[2px] bg-blue mb-2.5"></div>
      <div class="text-[18px] font-bold font-display">Ritji Ishaku</div>
      <div class="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/40 font-body mt-1">Clinical AI Automation Specialist</div>
    </div>

     <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center md:items-start gap-3 w-full md:w-auto">
        <a
          href="#contact"
          class="btn-primary group w-full md:w-auto justify-center"
          aria-label="Go to contact form"
        >
           Book your free 20-minute call →
        </a>
        <p class="text-[12px] text-white/60 font-body text-center md:text-left">
           No commitment required &nbsp;·&nbsp; Remote via WhatsApp &nbsp;·&nbsp; Available worldwide
        </p>
      </div>
  </div>
</section>
